title: Railworks TS2015 AP Class 158/159 Sound Pack
description:
As requested, updated sound pack. Scenario fix 04.10.2014 

During the installation process, these sounds will be applied to to the RS.com Class 158 and the class 158 included in the Liverpool to Manchester and Settle to Carlisle routes. Please note that the two-tone horn and user controlled buzzer will only be applied to the liveries included in these packs.



Please support the developers and buy some of their content if you can afford it.


If you would like to contribute, please read the Readme.pdf.


A Team tpb_4_ever upload
